LlamaForge
==========

LlamaForge is a graphical management wrapper for llama.cpp. It is an
independent project and is NOT affiliated with, endorsed by, or part of
the llama.cpp / ggml-org project.

LlamaForge builds and runs llama.cpp but contains no llama.cpp source code
itself; it invokes llama.cpp's own binaries and build system. When you use
LlamaForge to build llama.cpp, the resulting binaries are governed by
llama.cpp's own MIT license.

